Package: owmr
Title: OpenWeatherMap API Wrapper
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: person("Stefan", "Kuethe", email = "crazycapivara@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R Interface to OpenWeatherMap.
   Beside funcs for fetching weather data from owm, owmr supplies
   tools to tidy up fetched data (for fast and simple access) and to show it on leaflet maps.
URL:
  https://github.com/crazycapivara/owmr/,
  https://crazycapivara.github.io/owmr/
BugReports: https://github.com/crazycapivara/owmr/issues/
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
    magrittr,
    httr,
    jsonlite
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests:
    leaflet,
    whisker,
    testthat,
    covr
